  <entry>
    <title>NATS JetStream：消息队列的现代选择</title>
    <link href="/2026/04/05/nats-jetstream-introduction/"/>
    <url>/2026/04/05/nats-jetstream-introduction/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="NATS-JetStream：消息队列的现代选择"><a href="#NATS-JetStream：消息队列的现代选择" class="headerlink" title="NATS JetStream：消息队列的现代选择"></a>NATS JetStream：消息队列的现代选择</h1><p>NATS JetStream 是 NATS 的持久化消息系统，提供 at-least-once 和 exactly-once 语义。</p><h2 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h2><ul><li><strong>Stream</strong>：消息存储单元，可配置保留策略</li><li><strong>Consumer</strong>：订阅 stream 并消费消息的实体</li><li><strong>Subject</strong>：消息路由的主题</li></ul><h2 id="Go-客户端示例"><a href="#Go-客户端示例" class="headerlink" title="Go 客户端示例"></a>Go 客户端示例</h2><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs go"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;github.com/nats-io/nats.go/jetstream&quot;</span><br><br>nc, _ := nats.Connect(nats.DefaultURL)<br>js, _ := jetstream.New(nc)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 创建 stream</span><br>js.CreateStream(ctx, jetstream.StreamConfig&#123;<br>    Name:     <span class="hljs-string">&quot;EVENTS&quot;</span>,<br>    Subjects: []<span class="hljs-type">string</span>&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;events.&gt;&quot;</span>&#125;,<br>&#125;)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 发布消息</span><br>js.Publish(ctx, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;events.user.created&quot;</span>, []<span class="hljs-type">byte</span>(<span class="hljs-string">`&#123;&quot;user_id&quot;:&quot;123&quot;&#125;`</span>))<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 消费消息</span><br>cons, _ := js.CreateConsumer(ctx, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;EVENTS&quot;</span>, jetstream.ConsumerConfig&#123;<br>    Durable: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;processor&quot;</span>,<br>    AckPolicy: jetstream.AckExplicitPolicy,<br>&#125;)<br><br>msgs, _ := cons.Messages()<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> msg := <span class="hljs-keyword">range</span> msgs &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 处理消息</span><br>    msg.Ack()<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="与-Kafka-对比"><a href="#与-Kafka-对比" class="headerlink" title="与 Kafka 对比"></a>与 Kafka 对比</h2><p>NATS JetStream 部署简单、延迟更低，适合中小规模的事件驱动架构。</p>]]></content>
    
    
